510
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:16,260
Then, what about this car?

511
00:41:16,260 --> 00:41:18,470
Don't look down on this car.

512
00:41:18,470 --> 00:41:20,660
Even though it costs only about two or three hundred thousand,

513
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:23,320
I bought it with each penny I earned by myself

514
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:26,160
from my work-study jobs while I was in college.

515
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:29,820
So, when I can, I often drive this one.

516
00:41:29,820 --> 00:41:33,030
It brings to mind the days of my youth.

517
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:38,010
