519
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:45,970
- I can see that. 
 - Really?

520
00:41:47,410 --> 00:41:50,710
Do you know what the worst habit of the "second-generation rich" guy is?

521
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:52,840
It's their wealth.

522
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:55,010
But fortunately you aren't wealthy.

523
00:41:56,410 --> 00:41:59,480
