524
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:03,360
isn't that behavior a little shallow?

525
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,360
Do you think I'm shallow?

526
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:07,450
No, no, no. That's not what I meant.

527
00:42:07,450 --> 00:42:09,620
You're actually right. I am indeed shallow.

528
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:11,590
People all have their shortcomings.

529
00:42:11,590 --> 00:42:13,950
I don't think that's a shortcoming.

530
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:16,460
If a young woman

531
00:42:16,460 --> 00:42:19,400
