532
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:23,060
it's very possible that they will miss out on some valuable things.

533
00:42:23,060 --> 00:42:24,870
For example?

534
00:42:24,870 --> 00:42:29,560
For example, you could lose a man who is

535
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:32,540
